		  <section id="1.1 Introduction" level="3">
			  <title>1.1 Introduction</title>
			  <content>
				  <para>
					  Introduction on NTDS
					  <a onclick="javascript:parent.VideoFrame(&quot;../Author/Contents/NTDS/The_New_Torpedo_Defence_System/Technical_Manual/Video/videos/V1_intro_NTDS.mp4&quot;);parent.masterframe.rows=&quot;70%,30%&quot;" actuate="uSer">
						  Click here <img src="../Author/Contents/NTDS/The_New_Torpedo_Defence_System/Technical_Manual/Images/video.gif" style="height:40px;width:50px;" />
					  </a>
				  </para>
				  <para>
					  Mahindra Defence Systems (MDNS) has teamed exclusively
					  with Ultra Sonar Systems (Ultra) to deliver the Indian Navy’s New Torpedo
					  Defence System (NTDS).
				  </para>
				  <para>
					  The New Torpedo Defence System
					  (NTDS) has an extremely capable passive acoustic array and delivers
					  excellent classification performance against a wide range of torpedo
					  threats coupled with tailored countermeasure action response by launching
					  Expendable Acoustic Devices (EADs) from the Expendable Device Launcher
					  (EDL).
				  </para>
				  <para>
					  The NTDS consists of an Expendable Device Launcher
					  (EDL), Local Control Unit (LCU), Remote Control Unit (RCU) for EDL,
					  a Processing Cabinet, Display Console, and the Winch equipped with
					  a Fibre Optic Tow Cable (FOTC) array. The EDL is used to launch Expendable
					  Acoustic Devices (EADs) to counter the threat of incoming torpedoes
					  to ships. The Winch is used to deploy and recover the flexible FOTC
				  </para>
				  <para>
					  The illustration of the NTDS on a Warship is shown in Fig.
					  1.1.
				  </para>
				  <para>
					  <figure>
						  <graphic fileref="../Author/Contents/NTDS/The_New_Torpedo_Defence_System/Technical_Manual/Images/fig_1_1_1.gif"></graphic>
						  <figtitle>Fig. 1.1: Illustration of the NTDS on a Warship</figtitle>
					  </figure>
				  </para>
			  </content>
			  <section id="1.1.1 Frontispiece of the NTDS" level="4">
				  <title>1.1.1 Frontispiece of the NTDS</title>
				  <content>
					  <para>
						  <figure>
							  <graphic fileref="../Author/Contents/NTDS/The_New_Torpedo_Defence_System/Technical_Manual/Images/fig_1_1_2.gif"></graphic>
						  </figure>
