                See Fig. 1.76 for cable connections between
                Plinth, SRJB, MCP
              </para>
              <para>
                <figure>
                  <graphic
                  fileref="../Author/Contents/NTDS/The_New_Torpedo_Defence_System/Technical_Manual/Images/fig_1_76.gif"
  ></graphic>
                  <figtitle>
