							  the packing box as required:
						  </para>

						  <para>(i) Wooden board/pallet, plywood board (moisture resistant) as required</para>
						  <para>(ii) Slicagel – Dessicant</para>
						  <para>(iii) Rubber, Latex foam, sheets for packaging </para>
						  <para>(iv) Plywood board, moisture resistant</para>
						  <para>(v) Polyethylene, Air bubble film, 1 layer or 2 layers</para>
						  <para>(vi) Water proof thick polythene cover</para>
						  <para>(vii) Coir, Rubberised Pads for packaging</para>
						  <para>(viii) Tape, Polypropylene</para>
						  <para>(ix) Wood wool for packaging</para>
						  <para>(x) Strap made of PP (polypropylene) and PET (polyethylene terephthalate)</para>
						  <para>(xi) Strapping Tools Tensioner Sealer Cutter for polythene</para>



