				  <section id="2.2.6 Mounting Holes   " level="4">
					  <title>2.2.6 Mounting Holes</title>
					  <content>
						  <para>
							  The units shall be deck fastened or bulk-head fastened
							  by means of the mounting holes provided in the units.
						  </para>
					  </content>
				  </section>
				  <section id="2.2.7 Installation Material Quality  " level="4">
					  <title>2.2.7 Installation Material Quality </title>
					  <content>
						  <para>
							  All installation materials (screws, washers, nuts &amp;
							  bolts) shall satisfy the environmental requirements.
						  </para>
					  </content>
				  </section>
				  <section id="2.2.8 Paints" level="4">
					  <title>2.2.8 Paints</title>
					  <content>
						  <para>
							  The units of NTDS system are painted with light admiralty
							  grey color. The type of paint used is RAL7040 for weather deck units
							  and RAL 7032 (pebble grey) for units fitted in Operators Room/ Bridge.
						  </para
  >
					  </content>
				  </section>
				  <section id="2.2.9 Fire Fighting Requirements " level="4">
					  <title>2.2.9 Fire Fighting Requirements </title>
					  <content>
						  <para>
							  A fire in the equipment should never be extinguished
							  using water or a powder extinguisher to prevent the electronic circuit
							  or cabinet wiring from getting damaged. If a fire starts in the equipment,
							  the mains supply should be switched OFF immediately. Fire extinguishers
							  of CO2 type must be used to put out the fire.
						  </para>
					  </content>
				  </section>
				  <section id="2.2.10 Safety   " level="4">
					  <title>2.2.10 Safety</title>
					  <content>
						  <para>
							  Safety measures must be observed when installing, operating
							  or maintaining the equipment. For more details,<h6>
								  <a onclick="javascript:parent.showPDF(&quot;../Author/Contents/NTDS/The_New_Torpedo_Defence_System/Technical_Manual/Images/Safety.pdf&quot;);parent.masterframe.rows=&quot;70%,30%&quot;">
									  Click here.<img src="../Author/Contents/NTDS/The_New_Torpedo_Defence_System/Technical_Manual/Images/book.jfif" style="height:40px;width:50px;" />
								  </a>
							  </h6>
						  </para>
					  </content>
				  </section>
				  <section id="2.2.11 Environmental Specifications" level="4">
					  <title>2.2.11 Environmental Specifications</title>
					  <content>
						  <para>
							  The NTDS complies with environmental specifications
							  for ship-borne applications, as specified in JSS 55555:2012 (Rev.
							  03)
						  </para>
						  <para>
							  <ul type="DISC">
								  <li>
									  For Environmental Specifications of Launcher,<h6>
										  <a onclick="javascript:parent.showPDF(&quot;../Author/Contents/NTDS/The_New_Torpedo_Defence_System/Technical_Manual/Images/Launcher_ES.pdf&quot;);parent.masterframe.rows=&quot;70%,30%&quot;">
