														  <li>Local indicator ON.</li>
														  <li>Remote indicator Blinking.</li>
														  <li>Length and Depth indicator display previous value.</li>
														  <li>Drum rotating by Local Joystick.</li>
														  <li>Displacement for Level Wind Assembly by Local joystick.</li>
													  </ol>
												  </para>
											  </td>
										  </tr>
										  <tr>
											  <td>4.14</td>
											  <td>
												  <para>
													  Set the Local / Remote Switch at Remote Position and Remote
													  Connected.
												  </para>
												  <para>
													  Move Drum Joystick and Wind Level Joystick
													  for operation on Local Control Panel.
												  </para>
												  <para>
													  Level Joystick for
													  operation on Remote Control Panel.
												  </para>
											  </td>
											  <td>
												  <para>
													  <ol type="a">
														  <li>Supply available indicator ON</li>
														  <li>Emergency Stop indicator OFF</li>
														  <li>System Ready Indictor ON</li>
														  <li>Motor Over temperature indicator OFF</li>
														  <li>Local Indicator OFF</li>
														  <li>Remote indicator ON.</li>
														  <li>Length and Depth indicator display previous value.</li>
														  <li>Drum rotating by Remote Joystick. And not by Local Panel Joystick.</li>
														  <li>
															  Displacement for Level Wind Assembly by Remote joystick and not
