													  </ol>
												  </para>
											  </td>
										  </tr>
										  <tr>
											  <td>4.18</td>
											  <td>
												  Deploy the Tow till the 466 meters or less than that remains on
												  drum
											  </td>
											  <td>
												  <para>
													  <ol type="a">
														  <li>At Cabinet SW4 is in closed position.</li>
														  <li>At cabinet SW1, 2, 3 and SW5 are in Open condition.</li>
													  </ol>
												  </para>
											  </td>
										  </tr>
										  <tr>
											  <td>4.19</td>
											  <td>Deploy the Tow 200 meters </td>
											  <td>At cabinet SW1, 2, 3, 4 and 5 are in Open.</td>
										  </tr>
										  <tr>
											  <td>4.20</td>
											  <td>
												  <para>
													  Bring the motor in stop condition and release the Motor
													  electric Brake by Rotating Manual release (two) Allen Bolt at Brake
													  Assembly once at clockwise direction.
												  </para>
