													  Engage the Motor electric Brake
													  by Rotating Manual release (two) Allen Bolt at Brake Assembly once
													  at anti-clockwise direction.  Try to Rotate drum motor by Manual Handle
												  </para
>
											  </td>
											  <td>
												  <para>
													  <ol type="a">
														  <li>Drum can rotate manually in both directions.</li>
														  <li>Drum Cannot Rotate in any direction.</li>
