>
						  <para>
							  For Console Interface Connection Details,(<a
onclick="javascript:parent.showPDF(&quot;../Author/Contents/NTDS/The_New_Torpedo_Defence_System/Technical_Manual/Images/Plate_4_4.pdf&quot;);parent.masterframe.rows=&quot;70%,30%&quot;"
