                      <h6>Fault Diagnosis / Probable Cause</h6>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                      <h6>Remedial Action</h6>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td rowspan="2">1</td>
                    <td rowspan="2">
                      On LCU, indicator lamps fail to light when Lamp Test
                      switch is pushed.
                    </td>
                    <td>(a)	Lamp may be faulty.</td>
                    <td>
                      Press Lamp test push button provided on LCU and check if lamp
